				<div id="contenido">
				<p>
				<h2>SPECIAL SHIELDS AND EXTRAS</h2>
				<b>Armor Blades.</b> Whenever you succeed on a grapple check or are grappled by an enemy, that creature takes 3 <img src="sword.png"> damage.
				<br>
				<br>
				<br>
				<b>Armor Spikes.</b> Whenever you succeed on a grapple check or are grappled by an enemy, that creature takes 3 <img src="arrow.png"> damage.
				<br>
				<br>
				<br>
				<b>Brigandine armor.</b> For an additional 50 gold you can make so the armor ignores the stealth disadvantage.
				<br>
				<br>
				<br>
				<b>Shield Spikes.</b> If you have the Shield Master feat and utilize the ability to shove a creature, that creature takes 3 <img src="arrow.png"> damage.
				<br>
				<br>
				<br>
				<b>Skirmisher.</b> A successful shove using this shield deals d4 + STR mod as <img src="hammer.png"> damage
				<br>
				<br>
				<br>
				<b> Tower Shield. </b> You can’t make opportunity attacks while holding this shield.
				
				<br>
				
				<br>
				
				<br>
				<b>Wrist Buckler.</b> You can attack with a weapon held in the same arm that this shield is attached to and still gain the AC bonus. You can only wield a light weapon in whatever arm this shield is strapped to. Additionally you can use the versatile property on a weapon with this shield attatched and still gain the AC bonus
				<br>
				<br>
				<br>				
				</p>
				</div>
